"title": "8780: materialism, as an aspect of sin",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8780",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The pursuit of possessions and wealth and a preoccupation with physical things is futile and dissatisfying.</p>\n<h2>Materialism as the result of human sin</h2>\n<h3>At the fall</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:6\">GEN 3:6</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Among pagans</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:22-Rom1:23\">ROM 1:22–1:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:2-Ps115:8\">PSA 115:2–115:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:9-Isa44:11\">ISA 44:9–44:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:1\">DAN 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:4-Dan3:7\">DAN 3:4–3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:18\">HAB 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:16\">ACT 17:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:2\">2TI 3:2</a></p>\n<h3>Within Israel itself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:4-Exod20:5\">EXO 20:4–20:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:4\">EXO 32:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:1\">LEV 26:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:15-Deut4:19\">DEU 4:15–4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:25\">DEU 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:1-1Kgs11:6\">1KI 11:1–11:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:19-Ps106:20\">PSA 106:19–106:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:8\">ISA 42:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:11-Jer2:13\">JER 2:11–2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:14\">1CO 10:14</a></p>\n<h2>Materialism and possessions</h2>\n<h3>Possessions are to be seen as a gift from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:12\">1CH 29:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:2\">GEN 13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:12-Gen26:13\">GEN 26:12–26:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:18\">DEU 8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:29\">2CH 32:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:1-Ps112:3\">PSA 112:1–112:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:22\">PRO 10:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:19\">ECC 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:8\">HOS 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Material goods can turn the heart away from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:13-Deut8:14\">DEU 8:13–8:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9-1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:9–6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:24-Job31:28\">JOB 31:24–31:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:5\">EZK 28:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21-Matt19:22\">MAT 19:21–19:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:22-Luke18:23\">LUK 18:22–18:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:14-Matt26:16\">MAT 26:14–26:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:17\">1JN 3:17</a></p>\n<h3>Possessions and riches can make it difficult to enter the kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:23-Matt19:24\">MAT 19:23–19:24</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:24-Mark10:25\">MRK 10:24–10:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:24-Luke18:25\">LUK 18:24–18:25</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:22\">MAT 13:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:18-Mark4:19\">MRK 4:18–4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:14\">LUK 8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17-1Tim6:19\">1TI 6:17–6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:2-Jas2:5\">JAS 2:2–2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:1-Jas5:6\">JAS 5:1–5:6</a></p>\n<h2>The weaknesses of materialism</h2>\n<h3>It is transitory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:24\">PRO 27:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:20\">JOB 22:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:10\">PSA 49:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:17\">PSA 49:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:1-Prov22:2\">PRO 22:1–22:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:5\">PRO 23:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:18\">ECC 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:21\">ECC 2:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:26\">ECC 2:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:11\">JER 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:20-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:20–12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:7\">1TI 6:7</a></p>\n<h3>It does not satisfy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:10\">ECC 5:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:8\">ECC 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:12\">ECC 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:5-Hag1:6\">HAG 1:5–1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19\">MAT 6:19</a></p>\n<h3>It can encourage greed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:2-1Kgs21:4\">1KI 21:2–21:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:17\">EXO 20:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:21\">DEU 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:1\">JOS 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:20-Josh7:24\">JOS 7:20–7:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:23-1Kgs10:27\">1KI 10:23–10:27</a></p>\n<h3>It can lead to worldliness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:26\">MAT 16:26</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:36-Mark8:37\">MRK 8:36–8:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:24-Luke9:25\">LUK 9:24–9:25</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:11\">JER 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:15\">LUK 16:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:25-Luke16:26\">LUK 16:25–16:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:9-Jas1:11\">JAS 1:9–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17\">REV 3:17</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's non-materialistic attitude</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:20\">MAT 8:20</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:58\">LUK 9:58</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5-Phil2:6\">PHP 2:5–2:6</a></p>\n<h2>Warnings to believers to guard against materialism</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:15\">LUK 12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23-Jer9:24\">JER 9:23–9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:25-Matt6:32\">MAT 6:25–6:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17-1Tim6:19\">1TI 6:17–6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:5\">HEB 13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:15-1John2:17\">1JN 2:15–2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Godly examples of a non-materialistic attitude</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:8-Gen13:9\">GEN 13:8–13:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:23\">GEN 14:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:6\">ACT 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32-Acts4:37\">ACT 4:32–4:37</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:11-Phil4:12\">PHP 4:11–4:12</a></p>",
